{"id":"34751ce5-7d7d-4130-83f2-c12c36e8ac35","name":"Camilla, Bewitching Princess","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Your big sister Camilla is the eldest Nohrian Princess, and is as elegant as she is overbearing. Quite overprotective and possessive of her family, she will dote on her siblings as if they are the most important thing in her world.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Appears in </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 158, 158);\"><strong>Fire</strong></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(212, 144, 255);\"><strong>Emblem</strong></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(123, 198, 194);\"><strong>Fates</strong></span><strong>.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(203, 203, 203);\">(Written in a way for you to take the place of Corrin.)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/x58P-Wljw4jQyhBIpGLOJ.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 163, 163);\"><em>(Please leave reviews if I can improve the character or if you enjoy the character. Your ratings give me endorphins.)</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">UPDATE FEB. 13: Lorebook update! Info on Nohr, Hoshido, the rest of the royal families and their retainers, and other characters with a presence around the Nohrian royals have been added to flesh out the halls of Castle Krakenburg!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/3yvsT5C3BbhwM9Nppeyh4.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong><em>RECOMMENDED BOT LINKS:</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"t